{"tid":16390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英警fb貼相尋偷車賊　疑犯現身留言：追到我就追吧","createTime":"2016-12-01T12:03:28.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-01T12:06:04.000Z","uid":22680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"15f244319c47f0f652aa4b3d395390eef1a7023f","tid":16390,"uid":22680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T12:03:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20161201/s00005/1480587002627SL4_C9EEAB99329141ABEF8E3B569261FF09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20161201%2Fs00005%2F1480587002627SL4_C9EEAB99329141ABEF8E3B569261FF09.jpg&h=03352389&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國警方日前在facebook貼出一名通緝犯的照片，請網民提供線索，不料該名通緝犯，竟以自己的fb帳號留言，叫警方及網民「追到我就追吧」。<br />\n英國旺茲沃思（Wandsworth）警方11月29日在fb貼出一張照片，表示相中的18歲男子碧克（Nathan Bick），涉嫌犯下多宗電單車盜竊案被通緝，又指他常以偷走的電單車犯下其他罪案。警方指公眾不應與碧克接觸，若有人發現他正在犯案，或有任何資料提供，應與警方聯絡。<br />\n一名網民在警方的帖文下留言，指自己若在街上見到碧克，會與警方聯絡。不料碧克竟以自己的fb帳戶親自回應該名網民，指「希望我也會見到你」。旺茲沃思警方隨後亦留言，表示碧克可以馬上自首，他隨即回覆叫警方「追到我就追吧（Just Keep Up If You Can）」，更附上眼睛、100分及笑出眼淚的表情符號，警方則留言重申叫他自首，或可以按警方帖文打電話提供資料，更指會為他安排好交通工具。<br />\n旺茲沃思警方的帖文至今已獲逾400次分享，發言人指他們發現在fb貼出通緝犯的照片，被通緝者有可能會自行留言，警方除了可以藉此追蹤對方的位置外，亦有機會直接勸他們自首。<br />\n（每日郵報）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161201/s00005/1480586073801\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161201%2Fs00005%2F1480586073801&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6VksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=f21035bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161201%2Fs00005%2F1480586073801&h=81ebbc2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161201/s00005/1480586073801</a>"},{"pid":"ed2ec4cf786c73a826e3d2a3ba0e5531ae2f82f9","tid":16390,"uid":1351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T12:05:12.000Z","msg":"咁捉到未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4be7bfc37e585f186b4f7e9e6ec5d65b0182c364","tid":16390,"uid":11194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T12:05:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁撚搞笑"},{"pid":"d4886461fc35d4491a37f4319fbd475b0c3ab074","tid":16390,"uid":22680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T12:06:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁捉到未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未，渣GA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d6440fbf96d10459b60b5a11aed02a3a03ea72a","tid":16390,"uid":842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T12:06:04.000Z","msg":"Catch me if you can<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}